tipsMap.stormAdvanceBackupTimeIntro: Customize how long before an NWS weather event the aPower(s) should activate. Default automatic is recommended.
tipsMap.stormNoticeEnableIntro: Automatically activate backup power when an adverse weather events approaches, or decide each time whether to activate backup power when you receive an NWS alert.
tipsMap.stormHedgeIntro: With Storm Hedge enabled. the aGate will receive National Weather Service (NWS) warnings about approaching adverse weather events. The aGate will then prioritize charging the aPower(s) to 100%. If there is an outage. aPower will power household loads.
tipsMap.closeStormHedgeTip: With Storm Hedge disabled, the aGate will not receive National Weather Service (NWS) warnings about adverse weather events near your household.
